    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285420/extras/5708913c17f9c7040d4b04322f52fc23.poster.avif?t=1766057097\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285420/extras/5708913c17f9c7040d4b04322f52fc23.webm?t=1766057097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285420/extras/5708913c17f9c7040d4b04322f52fc23.mp4?t=1766057097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This warm and cute adventure platformer game will provide hours and hours of fun to both grownups and kids. A classic platformer jump and run game with huge levels, secrets to discover and treasures to collects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The evil countess turns Tibor into a vampire! Only, Tibor is an unique vampire - a kind one! A vampire whose love for Agnes is stronger than any other force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through dozens of exciting and rich levels, discover tons of secret locations, collect coins, diamonds and potions, all while enjoying beautiful landscapes in this fun platformer game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will appeal to both children and adults; it's just fun to jump around, discover new places, overcome obstacles and collect coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔎 What awaits you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Storybook charm: Based on a beloved Croatian fairy tale.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Smooth platforming: Improved controls with gamepad support even on your smartphone</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Kid-safe fun: No graphic violence — ideal for family play.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Collectibles &amp; secrets: Re-playable levels with exploration rewards.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285420/extras/7a81ee3039923cf539649dd1fd8ba88b.avif?t=1766057097\" width=630 height=170 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BASED on the popular Croatian fairy tale</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NO VIOLENCE; makes it perfect for all ages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DISCOVER 5 different worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DOZENS of huge levels to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIND many secret places and BONUS levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >COLLECT coins, diamonds, potions and other treasures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BEAUTIFUL 4K ultra HD graphics</p></li></ul>",
